These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, soul, hip-hop, country, classical
6 different games are played: canasta, whist, go, poker, bridge, snooker
1. the fan hip-hop is on the left of the fan soul##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the fan classical##1
3. the fan d&b is on the left of the fan electronic##1
4. the person playing bridge is between the fan classical and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person playing poker is between the person playing bridge and the person playing whist##2
6. the person playing canasta is the fan hip-hop##1
7. the fan country is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the left of the fan electronic##1
9. the fan country is on the right of the fan classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Music-Genre           | d&b | electronic | classical | country | hip-hop    | soul  |
| Game   | snooker | whist   | poker       | bridge        | canasta | go |

