.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, prince, bolivar, dannemann, ritmeester, pall-mall
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, marigold, orchid, sunflower, lily
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person who growsorchid is between the dannemann-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growslily##1
7. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
8. the prince-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Cigar   | prince | pall-mall | ritmeester | dannemann | bolivar | aristoff  |
| Flower           | lily | sunflower  | iris | aconite    | orchid  | marigold |

