.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, cooking, hiking, chess, traveling
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, spy, crime, family, scientific, disaster
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person watching action movies##2
7. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | traveling      | chess | hiking | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | disaster  | action | family   | scientific       | crime |

