.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: aquamarine, chestnut, blue, orange, emerald, lilac
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, march, september, may, april, october
1. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who likes lilac##2
7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Color        | chestnut    | lilac | blue | aquamarine | emerald | orange   |
| Birthday   | may | april        | march  | january     | october  | september |

