.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, august, april, march, june, november
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, almond-milk, cola, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in june##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Birthday   | may   | march    | november | april | august | june   |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | juice | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | cola  | sprite |

