.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: white, blue, red, blood-red, amber, azure
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, chaman, bluemaster, dannemann, game, swisher
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
2. the swisher-smoker is the person who likes blue##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the right of the game-smoker##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
7. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who likes azure##1
8. the person who likes red is between the person who likes blood-red and the swisher-smoker##2
9. the person who likes white is the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Color    | white | azure | amber  | blood-red      | red | blue  |
| Cigar   | chaman  | bluemaster    | dannemann | dunhill | game | swisher |

