.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
6 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, guinea-pig, lizard, rat, cat
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, software-developer, social-worker, journalist, pilot
1. the social-worker is the social-worker##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the lizard##2
4. the owner of the lizard is the pilot##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the owner of the rat is between the social-worker and the journalist##2
7. the social-worker is on the right of the analyst##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the right of the social-worker##1
9. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Pet       | cat | lizard | hedgehog | rat | guinea-pig | horse |
| Job   | software-developer | pilot    | journalist  | analyst    | social-worker    | freelancer    |

