1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who likes green is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes amber##2
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes red##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in december##2
6. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes green##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Birthday           | june | february | december | april | september | may |
| Color   | red   | orange   | coral         | amber    | green     | blood-red     |

