 3. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the colombian##1
 5. the french is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the colombian##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the thai is on the left of the mexican##1
 9. the argentine is on the left of the thai##1
10. the mexican is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
