.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
City: paris, hannover, boston, san-francisco, berlin, new-york
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: surfing, ice-hockey, handball, skateboarding, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person traveling to hannover##2
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person traveling to new-york and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is between the person who's sport is handball and the person traveling to boston##2
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| City   | san-francisco     | paris | berlin   | boston     | new-york       | hannover       |
| Sport    | ice-hockey | skateboarding   | surfing | water-polo | weightlifting | handball |

