.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-17::.
6 different games are played: go, snooker, backgammon, monopoly, domino, whist
There 6 different types of food: eggplant, cherry, pepper, artichoke, broccoli, asparagus
1. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person playing domino##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing go is on the far left##1
4. the person eating broccoli is the person playing go##1
5. the person playing whist is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing snooker##2
6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
7. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
9. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |       5       |   6    |
| Game   | go | monopoly      | domino       | backgammon    | whist          | snooker    |
| Food         | broccoli  | eggplant | asparagus | cherry | pepper | artichoke |

