 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the prince-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is between the swisher-smoker and the blend-smoker##2
10. the havana-smoker is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | blend | montecristo | swisher | havana | prince |
| Pet   | pony | dog | lizard      | goldfish     | guinea-pig       | chinchilla |

 